      <title>Obama Faces Tough Choice Between Turkey and Kurds</title>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Feb 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>Akbar Shahid Ahmed</author>
      <link>https://www.newsdeeply.com/syria/articles/2016/02/17/obama-faces-tough-choice-between-turkey-and-kurds</link>
      <guid>https://www.newsdeeply.com/syria/articles/2016/02/17/obama-faces-tough-choice-between-turkey-and-kurds</guid>
      <description>Turkey’s war against Kurdish insurgents has turned into open hostilities with the Syrian Kurdish minority, judged by Ankara to be connected to the militant Kurdistan Workers’ Party (PKK). Washington must choose between its NATO ally and its most effective ground force in the battle against ISIS.</description>
