      <author>Akbar Shahid Ahmed</author>
      <link>https://www.newsdeeply.com/syria/articles/2016/02/01/without-political-support-u-s-kurd-alliance-in-jeopardy</link>
      <guid>https://www.newsdeeply.com/syria/articles/2016/02/01/without-political-support-u-s-kurd-alliance-in-jeopardy</guid>
      <description>Although the United States has been closely courting Syrian Kurds over the past year, increasingly relying on them as a ground force in the battle against ISIS, the fact that the U.S. has tacitly allowed Turkey to bar any Kurdish presence at the table in Geneva may jeopardize the alliance.</description>
